[0.460, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[2D\u001b[4B\r\u001b[5A  HTTP request hits a provider adapter at the edge (signature verification + normalize to CloudEvent). The   \r\u001b[1B  CloudEvent\u001b[1Cthen\u001b[1Cflows\u001b[1Cthrough\u001b[1Ca\u001b[1Clinear\u001b[1Cpipeline:\u001b[1CSchema\u001b[1CValidator\u001b[1C→\u001b[1CDedup\u001b[1C→\u001b[1CRouter\u001b[1C→\u001b[1CHandler.\u001b[1CThe\u001b[1CRouter\u001b[1Cis\r\u001b[1B   a registry mapping \u001b[38;2;177;185;249m(ce.type, ce.source)\u001b[39m patterns to handler functions — configured, not hardcoded.        \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDead-letter storage taps in at two points: validation failures and handler failures, each with reason    \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcodes.                                  \r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[38;2;136;136;136m─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\r\r\n\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m❯ \u001b[39m\u001b[7m \u001b[27m\r\r\n\u001b[38;2;136;136;136"]
