[0.886, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[2D\u001b[4B\r\u001b[5A  - \u001b[1mCloudEvents envelope overhead for simple payloads\u001b[22m -- Wrapping a GitHub PR webhook (already               \r\u001b[1B  well-structured\u001b[1CJSON)\u001b[1Cin\u001b[1Ca\u001b[1CCloudEvents\u001b[1Cenvelope\u001b[1Cadds\u001b[1Cmetadata\u001b[1Cfields\u001b[1Cand\u001b[1Ca\u001b[1Cparsing\u001b[1Cstep.\u001b[1CFor\u001b[1Ctwo\u001b[1Cproviders\r\u001b[1B  this is negligible, but at scale the normalization cost compounds. Mitigation: adapter benchmarks in the   \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsteel thread.                                                                                            \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B                                                     \r\r\n\u001b[38;2;136;136;136m─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\r\r\n\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m❯ \u001b[39m\u001b[7m \u001b[27m\r\r\n\u001b[38;2;136;136;136m──────"]
